{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/2011/07/dynamic-languages-dlr-languages-ug","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Kevin McKelvin"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2cf33cb0-c1a5-52f4-9eba-121f8ef391cf","excerpt":"Thanks for the great turn-out at the Microsoft Community Night on 12 July, we had a full room for the languages UG! For those who weren’t there - I gave a talk…","html":"<p>Thanks for the great turn-out at the Microsoft Community Night on 12 July, we had a full room for the languages UG!</p>\n<p>For those who weren’t there - I gave a talk on Dynamic Languages and the DLR on Tuesday 12 July.</p>\n<p>Here are the resources from the talk:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>IronPython: <a href=\"http://ironpython.codeplex.com\">http://ironpython.codeplex.com</a></li>\n<li>Clay: <a href=\"http://clay.codeplex.com/\">http://clay.codeplex.com</a></li>\n<li>System.Dynamic: <a href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/system.dynamic.aspx\">http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/system.dynamic.aspx</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>And here’s the code used to call a Python script from C#, using the DLR interop and dynamic keyword:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> engine <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> IronPython<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Hosting<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Python<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">CreateEngine</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> scope <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> engine<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Runtime<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">UseFile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"greeter.py\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">dynamic</span> greeterClass <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> scope<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">GetVariable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Greeter\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">dynamic</span> greeter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">greeterClass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">dynamic</span> s <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> greeter<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayHello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Kevin!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nConsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">WriteLine</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nConsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Read</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Dynamic Languages & DLR Presentation - Languages UG","date":"14 July 2011","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2011-07-14-dynamic-languages-dlr-languages-ug/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2011-06-21-entity-framework-4-1-hooks-drying-it-up-efhooks/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Entity Framework 4.1 Hooks – DRYing it up with EFHooks","date":"2011-06-21 19:05:38","slug":"entity-framework-4-1-hooks-drying-it-up-efhooks","draft":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2011-08-09-devs4devs-joburg-13-august/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Devs4Devs Jo'burg - 13 August","date":"2011-08-09 17:19:22","slug":"devs4devs-joburg-13-august","draft":null}}}}}